      "summary": "Yang on AI labour displacement. Key claims: UBI must precede UHI — no path to universal high income without political realignment first. 20–50% of 70M US office workers displaced in 12–18 months. College premium 'quickly evaporating' — unemployment rate for recent graduates now over 50%. 'The only career path you can rely on is entrepreneurship, but most people aren't cut out for that.' Trades safe for 10+ years ('robot plumbers not coming'). Velocity mismatch between technology and institutions: DC on 'catastrophic tape delay.' Elon's dual prediction: both universal high income AND social unrest. Dario/Anthropic acknowledged 50% entry-level white-collar job automation in 1–5 years — Yang: 'Thank goodness they came out and said it.' AI companionship cited as a factor in birth rate collapse. Strong evidence for T10 (job displacement) and T23 (abundance displacement).",
