      "summary": "Emil Michael (DoW CTO) at American Dynamism Summit. 'Holy cow moment': Anthropic contracts embedded in Pentagon systems (Central Command, IndoPacom, SouthCom) had dozens of restrictions including a potential kill-switch on combat operations. Post-Maduro raid (described as 'one of the most successful military operations of our lifetime'), an Anthropic senior exec asked whether their software was used — 'chill goes up your spine.' Moved from single-threaded vendor to multi-vendor approach. 80,000 → 1.2M DoW AI users in 90 days. 'If you don't believe in the system, you're taking upon yourself to be God.' Google Project Maven as cautionary parallel — now one of government's best partners. Simple requirements + firm fixed price replacing cost-plus contract model.",
