      "postPotentialReasoning": "The platform divergence angle — ChatGPT/Claude/Gemini splitting into different market positions — reframes the winner-take-all question for enterprise leaders making platform bets. Counter-intuitive: more competition at the top creates more opportunity in the middle.",
