      "postPotentialReasoning": "The harness analogy is immediately transferable to enterprise strategy. The 'token budgets as IT line item' critique names a specific organisational failure pattern that Scott's audience will recognise. Azhar's personal 150k→870m token consumption growth is a concrete, shocking data point.",
