          "url": "https://www.exponentialview.co/p/solving-problems-with-the-karpathy",
          "content": "Karpathy's AutoResearch: '700 ML experiments in two days' yielding '20 genuine improvements and an 11% speedup.' Toby Lutke (Shopify CEO) used it to develop 'a small machine learning model that beat ones that were twice the size.' Azhar extended to knowledge work: tasks 'going to take a week' completed 'in perhaps an hour.' Ran 'about 19 iterations' of thesis sharpening. Explicit framing: 'This is a reduction in the cost of the scientific method.'"
