          "content": "Sanders-AOC data centre moratorium: pause all construction nationwide until 'strong national safeguards' — protections for workers/consumers, environmental harms, civil rights. AOC's support significant: 'zero mentions of data centers and only a single post about AI' previously; by co-sponsoring she is 'declaring a position for the broader progressive movement.' Warner rejects moratorium ('idiocy') but supports codifying Anthropic red lines on domestic surveillance and autonomous weapons: 'Those should be policy decisions, not left to a single individual.' Manus CEO Xiao Hong and chief scientist Jie Yu Xiao barred from leaving China pending review of Meta's $2B acquisition — CCP treating domestic AI companies as national assets. China Computer Federation warned researchers against attending NeurIPS."
